msgid "Views"
msgstr "视图"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:10
msgid "View Global/Local"
msgstr "全局/局部 视图"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:12
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:68
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Mode:     All modes"
msgstr "模式:     所有模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`View --> View Global/Local`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`视图 --> 全局/局部 视图`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`NumpadSlash`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`NumpadSlash`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:19
msgid ""
"Global view shows all of the 3D objects in the scene. Local view isolates the selected "
"object or objects, so that they are the only ones visible in the viewport. This is useful "
"for working on objects that are obscured by other ones, or to speed up viewport performance "
"in heavy scenes."
msgstr ""
"全局视图显示了场景中的所有3D物体。局部视图将所选物体或物体独立显示，这样它们是在视图中唯一可"
"见的对象。对处理被其他物体遮住的物体很有用，或者加速大场景中视图性能很管用。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can toggle between *Global* and *Local View* by selecting the option from the *View "
"Menu* or using the shortcut :kbd:`NumpadSlash`."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 *全局视图* 和 *局部视图* 之间切换，从 *视图菜单* 中选择该选项或者使用快捷键 :kbd:"
"`NumpadSlash`."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:31
msgid "Global View."
msgstr "全局视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:36
msgid "Local View."
msgstr "局部视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:40
msgid "These notes cover changes in local-view which are not immediately obvious."
msgstr "这些注释涵盖了局部视图的中一些不明显的区别。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:43
msgid "3D Cursor"
msgstr "3D 游标"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:43
msgid ""
"In local-view the 3D cursor is not locked to the scene. Instead, each view has an "
"independent cursor location."
msgstr "在局部视图中，3D游标不会被锁定在场景中。相反，每个视图都有一个独立的游标位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:50
msgid "Layers"
msgstr "层"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:46
msgid ""
"Local-view bypasses layers, using only the selected objects when entering local-view. "
"Although new objects may be added while in local-view."
msgstr "局部视图绕过层, 在进入局部视图时只使用所选的物体. 虽然在本地视图中可以添加新物体。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:49
msgid ""
"It's also possible to send objects out of local view, using :menuselection:`Object --> Move "
"Objects out of Local View`, which can be useful to further isolate a selection."
msgstr ""
"也可以将物体从局部视图中发送出去，, 使用 :menuselection:`物体 --> 移出局部视图`, 这对于进一"
"步独立显示所选对象是很有用的。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:54
msgid "Preview Renders"
msgstr "预览设置"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:53
msgid ""
"Preview renders will still use lamps outside the local-view, this allows you to quickly "
"render previews without having to remember to select all lamps when entering local-view."
msgstr ""
"预览渲染仍然会使用局部视图以外的灯光,这样你就可以快速地渲染预览，而不必记住在进入局部视图时"
"选择所有的灯。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:59
msgid ""
"Accidentally pressing :kbd:`NumpadSlash` can happen rather often if you are new to Blender, "
"so if a bunch of the objects in your scene seem to have mysteriously vanished, try turning "
"off local view."
msgstr ""
"如果你是新手,不小心按下 :kbd:`NumpadSlash` 就会发生。 如果你的场景中有一堆东西神秘地消失了。"
"那就试试关闭局部视图模式。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:66
msgid "Quad View"
msgstr "四视图"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Menu:     :menuselection:`View --> Toggle Quad View`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`视图--> 切换四格视图`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Panel:    :menuselection:`Properties region --> Display --> Toggle Quad View`"
msgstr "面板:    :menuselection:`属性区域 --> 显示 --> 切换四格视图`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Q`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Q`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:76
msgid ""
"Toggling Quad View will split the 3D View into four views: Three *Orthographic* \"side views"
"\" and one *Camera*/*User View*. This view will allow you to instantly see your model from "
"a number of view points. In this arrangement, you can zoom and pan each view independently "
"but you cannot rotate the view."
msgstr ""
"切换四视图将把3D视图分成4个视图: 3个 *正交* \"侧视图\" 和一个 *摄像机*/*用户视图*. 这个视图"
"将允许您从多个视图点立即看到您的模型. 在这种安排中, 您可以独立缩放和平移每个视图，但是不能旋"
"转视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:83
msgid "Shortcuts for all views at once:"
msgstr "所有视图的快捷键："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:84
msgid "View All :kbd:`Ctrl-Home`"
msgstr "显示场景中所有物体 :kbd:`Ctrl-Home`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:85
msgid "View Selected :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadPeriod`"
msgstr "将选择对象移动到视图中心 :kbd:`Ctrl-NumpadPeriod`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:89
msgid ""
"Quad View is different from :doc:`splitting the area </interface/window_system/areas>` and "
"aligning the view manually. In Quad View, the four views are still part of a single 3D "
"View. So they share the same draw options and layers."
msgstr ""
"四视图不同于 :doc:`分割区域 </interface/window_system/areas>` 并手动对齐视图. 在四视图中, 这"
"四个视图仍然是单个3D视图的一部分. 所以它们有相同的绘制选项和图层。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:95
msgid "Quad View."
msgstr "四视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:99
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:101
msgid "These options can be found in :menuselection:`Properties region --> Display`."
msgstr "这些选项可以在 :menuselection:`属性区域 --> 显示` 中找到."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:103
msgid "Lock"
msgstr "锁定"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:104
msgid "If you want to be able to rotate each view, you can un-check the *Locked* option."
msgstr "如果您希望能够旋转每一个视图，您可以取消勾选 *锁定* 选项。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:105
msgid "Box"
msgstr "方框"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:106
msgid "Syncs the view position between side views."
msgstr "同步侧视图之间的视图位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:109
msgid "Clip"
msgstr "范围"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/views.rst:108
msgid "Clip objects based on what is visible in other side views."
msgstr "基于其他侧视图的可见区域来裁剪物体的显示结果。"
